content.text: Parameters: - (EnhancedGTMOSystem): Active instance of GTMØ v2 system - (bool): Whether to display attractor positions Features: - Color-coded particles based on entropy levels - Marked attractor positions with distinct symbols - Interactive 3D rotation and zoom - Colorbar indicating entropy scale
